    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that's ready to hit the road today? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s been really well-maintained and still runs like a dream, though it has a little bit of character from our adventures together. It\u2019s perfect for someone who wants a solid, comfy vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for it to go to a great home, so come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
