    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a driver-focused example of the legendary S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six delivers linear power delivery to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, addressing common E46 chassis fatigue points. The suspension retains its communicative geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the high-revving 8,000 RPM redline is matched by precise lateral control. While the aesthetics show honest signs of spirited road use, the mechanical vitals remain robust, featuring individual throttle bodies that are perfectly synced for optimal throttle response.",
