    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been my reliable daily driver and has been maintained with a 'no-expense-spared' philosophy. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical of careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the leather seats show light softening and natural creasing but are free of tears or stains. All electronics, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. It has a complete service log, with the most recent oil change and brake inspection performed just last month. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, and the engine runs smoothly without any unusual noises or leaks. This is a solid, honest car that bridges the gap between a showroom piece and a dependable traveler. It comes with two sets of keys and all original manuals.",
      "price": 34500.0,
