    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014very well-maintained and runs like a dream! This car is perfect for someone looking for a dependable, stylish vehicle that's ready for many more adventures. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
